        {
          "text": "has the lowest durability of any hero but has the longest basic attack range in the game, enough to destroy a defensive tower outside its range."
        },
        {
          "text": "can also attack defensive turrets from outside their range with."
        },
        {
          "text": "and are the only Marksmen who are unplayable in Mayhem Mode."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only hero who never uses hands in any attack."
        },
        {
          "text": "He is also the only hero with the sport-related mode of attacking."
        },
        {
          "text": "He is the only mechanical marksman in the game, having mechanical legs, although his other skins are human."
        },
        {
          "text": "Marksman is the only category of heroes that exclusively features Human or Humanoid heroes (such as Elves), with the only possible exceptions being, having non-human legs for being a Yasson, and in his wolf form."
        },
        {
          "text": "is considered to be the most difficult marksman because of her affecting her  can't be activated unless she hits all the weakness points on the target in 3 directions which will benefit her with her passive."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only hero who has 5 abilities. He is the only hero which always accompanied by his pet resulting in a 2v1 situation."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only marksman hero in the game who can charge his and he is also the slowest marksman."
